section.section:
"Home health care" means any of the following services that are provided under the general direction of a licensed health professional practicing within the scope of their practice:
Audiology and speech pathology;
Dietary and nutritional services;
Drug services;
Home health aid;
Laboratory;
Medical social services;
Nursing;
Occupational therapy;
Physical therapy; or
Provision of medically necessary sickroom equipment and supplies.
